{"type": "article", "id": 19935, "title": "Comics 沙发", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-30T07:20:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153951VpNl93Bd72wKmsSx.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t英国出生的插画家 Jon Burgerman 画了这些五颜六色的涂鸦，被法国的家具品牌 Ligne Roset 用在了沙发上，并重新命名为 Comics。沙发的造型像松软的枕头，各种颜色的粗细线条在上面交叉重叠，可以看到漫画角色的五官和肢体。看似杂乱，却在颜色上有巧妙的平衡，令人过目难忘，也能让周围环境变得活泼。他们的经典产品 Calin 也可以选择这款颜色。<a href=\"http://www.kirkbydesign.com/collections/kirkby-design-x-jon-burgerman/rainbow-scrawl\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261502572dkBKXpysNTZMva5.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150258j9SZgzpvyo6snEHm.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150259OdJa51WhCNs6IYDU.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150300YRbvntL9Jl8OBMxg.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"400\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}